## 🔧 Customization Guide

Want to personalize the website? Edit `index.html`:

### Change Names
Find and replace:
```html
<h1>Ray & Anne</h1>
```

### Change Messages
Edit the timeline section (search for "How It Began"):
```html
<p>The moment I met you, Anne...</p>
```

### Change Colors
Edit the `:root` CSS variables at the top:
```css
--primary-orange: #FF8C42;      /* Main orange */
--dark-orange: #E65100;         /* Darker orange */
--light-orange: #FFB088;        /* Lighter orange */
```

### Add More Timeline Items
Copy and paste this template:
```html
<div class="timeline-item">
    <div class="timeline-content">
        <h4>📅 Your Title</h4>
        <p>Your story here...</p>
    </div>
</div>
```

